{"article_id":"NnWfH0hYgiQVrTka","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"In a warning last summer to the regime of Syrian President Bashar al-Assad , President Obama said","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"a \" red line \" would have been crossed","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"if chemical weapons were used against rebels","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"fighting there ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"and he promised \" enormous consequences \"","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"if that were to happen .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"According to news reports Thursday and a direct statement by the White House ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that red line clearly has been crossed","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"with chemical weapons","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"used to kill between 100 and 150 people .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"But the White House was vague about its immediate response ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"other than to note","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"it would `` increase the scope and scale of assistance '' to the anti-Assad rebels .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"\" Following a deliberative review ,","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"our intelligence community assesses","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"that the Assad regime has used chemical weapons ,","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"including the nerve agent sarin ,","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"on a small scale against the opposition multiple times in the last year , \"","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"White House Deputy National Security Adviser Ben Rhodes said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"\" Our intelligence community has high confidence in that assessment","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"given multiple , independent streams of information . \"","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"\" The intelligence community estimates","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"that 100 to 150 people have died from detected chemical weapons attacks in Syria to date ;","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"however , casualty data is likely incomplete , \"","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"Mr. Rhodes said ,","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"indicating","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"that there may well be more casualties from chemical weapons .","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"\" The body of information","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"used","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"to make this intelligence assessment","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"includes reporting regarding Syrian officials","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"planning and executing regime chemical weapons attacks ; reporting","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"that includes descriptions of the time , location , and means of attack ; and descriptions of physiological symptoms","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"that are consistent with exposure to a chemical weapons agent , \"","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"Rhodes said .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"In his earlier warning to Syria , Obama had said this :","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"\" We have been very clear to the Assad regime","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"but also to other players on the ground","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"that a red line for us is we start seeing a whole bunch of chemical weapons","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"being moved around or utilized .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"There would be enormous consequences","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"if we start seeing movements on the chemical weapons or use ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that would change my calculations significantly . \"","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"\" A whole bunch of chemical weapons \" and \" change my calculations significantly \" are phrases","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"designed for maximum flexibility .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"But Obama has been under increasing pressure","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"to do more about the situation in Syria ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"which has seen ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"according to the latest UN estimate ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"at least 93,000 people killed","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"- most of them civilians -","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"and thousands more turned into refugees","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"trying to escape the fighting .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"In recent weeks , Britain , France , Israel , and the United Nations all have asserted","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"that Assad regime forces had used chemical weapons .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Domestic political pressure has been mounting as well .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"\" It is long past time","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"to bring the Assad regime ' s bloodshed in Syria to an end , \"","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Buck Brendan , spokesman for House Speaker John Boehner , said in a statement Thursday .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"\" As President Obama examines his options ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"it is our hope","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"he will properly consult with Congress","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"before taking any action . \"","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"In a joint statement , Senators John McCain","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"( R )","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"of Arizona and Lindsey Graham","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"( R )","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"of South Carolina ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"who are pushing for the US and its allies to establish a no-fly zone in Syria ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"said ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"\" We can not afford to delay any longer . \"","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"\" Assad is on the offensive with every weapon in his arsenal and with the complete support of his foreign allies , \"","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"they said .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"\" We must take more decisive actions now","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"to turn the tide of the conflict in Syria . \"","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"More to the point for a Democratic President in the White House , former President Bill Clinton this week sided with that view ,","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"according to several reports from a private meeting","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"at which Senator McCain and Mr. Clinton spoke .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"\" Some people say ,","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"' Okay , see what a big mess it is ?","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"Stay out ! '","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"I think","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"that ' s a big mistake , \"","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"Clinton said .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"\" I agree with you about this , \"","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"Clinton told McCain during an event for the McCain Institute for International Leadership in Manhattan Tuesday night ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"Politico.com reported .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"\" Sometimes it ' s just best to get caught trying ,","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"as long as you don ' t overcommit . \"","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"At this point , the Obama administration is being less than specific in its response the \" red line \" report about chemical weapons","depth":3},{"id":90,"text":"killing rebel fighters and likely civilians in Syria .","depth":3},{"id":91,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":92,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":94,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":95,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":96,"text":"\" The Assad regime should know","depth":4},{"id":97,"text":"that its actions have led us to increase the scope and scale of assistance","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"that we provide to the opposition , \"","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"Ben Rhodes at the White House said .","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"\" These efforts will increase going forward . \"","depth":5},{"id":101,"text":"\" The United States and the international community have a number of other legal , financial , diplomatic , and military responses available , \"","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"Rhodes said .","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"\" We are prepared for all contingencies ,","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"and we will make decisions on our own timeline . \"","depth"